Distribution.
Known from rainforest of the Australian Wet Tropics (WET) IBRA bioregion [Zones 7, 8, 9, 10, and 12] from around Lamb Range to Cardstone (~ 
160 km
) (
Fig. 17A
). Most specimens are from high elevations (
750–1250 m
). BIOCLIM modelling broadly reflects the species occurrence (
Fig. 17D
).
